 1 cup Lemon Juice &lt;li&gt; 1 cup Sugar &lt;li&gt; 6 Cups of Water (2 cups warm water, 4 cups cold water) &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/html&gt;" method: "&lt;html&gt; &lt;ol&gt; &lt;li&gt; Pour 2 cups of warm water into a pitcher and stir in sugar until it dissolves. &lt;li&gt; Pour in lemon juice, stir again, and add 4 cups of cold water. &lt;li&gt; Chill or serve over ice cubes. &lt;/ol&gt; &lt;/html&gt;" } }
